{"root":{"data":{"id":"dhusbkm4ze80","created":1776363540088,"text":"AI场景"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuscs1a2hc0","created":1776363634605,"text":"AI拍照识图购件","layout_mind_offset":{"x":27,"y":-188}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhusd6cczl40","created":1776363665750,"text":"客户对整机和零件进行拍照，AI识别零件型号和物料号，自助查询当前库存，价格以及替代件","resource":["解决客户/销售不认识零件号，减少人工查件"]},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhusfhgpt9k0","created":1776363846686,"text":"AI仓库拍照查库位","layout_mind_offset":{"x":25,"y":-82}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhusg63gdbc0","created":1776363900304,"text":"仓库管理员拍零件或者标签，自动显示库位，库存，库龄","layout_right_offset":{"x":15,"y":7},"resource":["不用搜系统，不用记编码"]},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhushn8aa080","created":1776364015965,"text":"AI整机拍照","layout_mind_offset":{"x":485,"y":95}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhusi4repgw0","created":1776364054127,"text":"拍挖掘机或者起重机，识别机型、吨位、年款、配置；或扫整机铭牌，出现整机档案，BOM清单，维修历史，常用易损件","layout_right_offset":{"x":879,"y":3}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhusk7x7fp40","created":1776364217736,"text":"AI问答","layout_mind_offset":{"x":478,"y":148}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuskh49vpk0","created":1776364237755,"text":"员工询问：报销怎么走，采购要找谁，签证材料，租房申请等等，AI给出标准流程，材料清单，以及新建流程的链接等","layout_right_offset":{"x":851,"y":1}},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}